---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="5 分钟快速安装 OpenClaw - 龙虾助理">
  <h1>📥 5 分钟快速安装 OpenClaw</h1>
  <p class="tag">新手入门 第 2 篇</p>

  <div class="toc">
    <h3>📑 目录</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#windows">Windows 安装</a></li>
      <li><a href="#macos">macOS 安装</a></li>
      <li><a href="#linux">Linux 安装</a></li>
      <li><a href="#api-key">配置 API Key</a></li>
      <li><a href="#faq">常见问题</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h2 id="windows">🪟 Windows 安装</h2>
  <h3>前置要求</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Windows 10/11</li>
    <li>Node.js 18+</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">1</span>
    <h3>安装 Node.js</h3>
    <p>访问 <a href="https://nodejs.org/" target="_blank">https://nodejs.org/</a> 下载 LTS 版本</p>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">2</span>
    <h3>安装 OpenClaw</h3>
    <pre><code>npm install -g openclaw</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">3</span>
    <h3>初始化</h3>
    <pre><code>mkdir my-assistant && cd my-assistant
openclaw init</code></pre>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <h2 id="macos">🍎 macOS 安装</h2>
  <h3>前置要求</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>macOS 10.15+</li>
    <li>Homebrew (推荐)</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">1</span>
    <h3>安装 Node.js</h3>
    <pre><code>brew install node</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">2</span>
    <h3>安装 OpenClaw</h3>
    <pre><code>npm install -g openclaw</code></pre>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <h2 id="linux">🐧 Linux 安装</h2>
  <h3>前置要求</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Ubuntu 20.04+ / Debian 11+ / CentOS 8+</li>
    <li>sudo 权限</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">1</span>
    <h3>安装 Node.js</h3>
    <pre><code>curl -fsSL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_20.x | sudo -E bash -
sudo apt-get install -y nodejs</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <span class="step-number">2</span>
    <h3>安装 OpenClaw</h3>
    <pre><code>sudo npm install -g openclaw</code></pre>
  </div>

  <hr/>

  <h2 id="api-key">配置 API Key</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>访问 <a href="https://bailian.console.aliyun.com/" target="_blank">阿里云百炼控制台</a></li>
    <li>创建 API Key</li>
    <li>配置文件位置：
      <ul>
        <li>Windows: <code>%APPDATA%\openclaw\config.json</code></li>
        <li>Mac/Linux: <code>~/.openclaw/config.json</code></li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ol>
  <pre><code>{
  "defaultModel": "bailian/qwen3.5-plus",
  "apiKey": "你的 API_KEY"
}</code></pre>

  <h2 id="faq">常见问题</h2>
  <div class="faq">
    <h3>❓ 安装失败？</h3>
    <pre><code>npm cache clean --force
npm install -g openclaw</code></pre>
  </div>

  <div class="faq">
    <h3>❓ 找不到命令？</h3>
    <p>将 npm 全局路径添加到 PATH 环境变量</p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq">
    <h3>❓ API Key 无效？</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>检查 Key 是否正确（无空格）</li>
      <li>确认账号有额度</li>
      <li>检查模型名称</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="nav-buttons">
    <a href="/guide/" class="btn btn-secondary">← 上一步</a>
    <a href="/guide/first-chat/" class="btn">下一步 →</a>
  </div>

  <style>
    .toc { background: #f9fafb; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.75rem; margin: 2rem 0; border-left: 4px solid #dc2626; }
    .toc h3 { margin-top: 0; }
    .toc ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
    .toc li { margin: 0.5rem 0; }
    .toc a { color: #374151; text-decoration: none; }
    .toc a:hover { color: #dc2626; text-decoration: underline; }
    .step { position: relative; padding-left: 4rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
    .step-number { position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; width: 2.5rem; height: 2.5rem; background: #dc2626; color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: bold; }
    .step h3 { margin-top: 0; }
    .faq { background: #f9fafb; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9; }
    .faq h3 { margin-top: 0; color: #0369a1; }
    .nav-buttons { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn-secondary { background: #6b7280; }
    pre { background: #1f2937; color: #f3f4f6; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; overflow-x: auto; }
    code { font-family: monospace; }
    hr { margin: 3rem 0; border: none; border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb; }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
